interpretation: The dodo emoji represents a sense of extinction or obsolescence. It can indicate that something that was once important or popular is no longer relevant or valued. The dodo also symbolizes a lack of awareness or foresight, as the bird was unable to adapt to changing environments and ultimately became extinct. When this card appears in a reading, it may suggest that the querent needs to let go of outdated ideas or practices in order to move forward. It could also indicate a warning to pay attention to potential threats or changes in their environment. Keywords associated with the dodo card include extinction, obsolescence, irrelevance, unawareness, and foresight.
